Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下我們再也找不到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突襲行動會有發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有任何線索  我們就能找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你來救我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪雅  羅文在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上次見他是什么時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們給你看了嗎  你父親關我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不合作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告訴我們你知道的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會怎么樣  你什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:00:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女兒來了  奧利維亞·波普就在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你們敢動我一根汗毛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等著收傳票吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴他們  麗芙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們嘗嘗你的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還沒起訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這侵犯了我的權力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我連自己被關在這的罪名都不知道是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謀殺  恐怖行動  叛國  多著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起訴她  把她關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗芙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力追捕  找到并殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你說了多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離我家遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道哈維一定很傷心  我只想解釋...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈維  你聯系過他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我兒子說過話了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在必須跟他談談
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-哈維  -他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在  -他去朋友家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就在房間里  我追蹤了他的手機信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寶貝  你還好嗎  哈維  你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對他做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是又跟他說了什么你是間諜的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是不是被你那通胡話嚇壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今我國境內的情況十分危急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們再不實行軍事干預...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國一定會致力保護西安哥拉的民主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證  大使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  總統先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝前來  大使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說吧  塞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想等到事后再來勸你  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我不愿發起戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們公然在我國境內發動襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們必須血債血償  這事必須有個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意  我們必須反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但兩個月后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當運輸機載著第一批士兵遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降落在多佛空軍基地時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就為了那充其量勉強稱得上的民主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒想好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到了再來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}奎恩·鉑金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收到我信息了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奎恩  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫比亞克死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他發現了哈克藏身在他的監視車里并襲擊了他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈克殺了庫比亞克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那他...  -他沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈克監視的是伊麗莎白·諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  麗芙  他們之間有來往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫比亞克  伊麗莎白·諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個你絕對想不到的人  副總統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國副總統  你確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我親眼所見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且諾斯和副總統有一腿  麗芙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是我親眼所見  簡直不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還在監視伊麗莎白·諾斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得先照顧哈克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我繼續監視她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  當我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊麗莎白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么能幫到你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能  或者該說  是不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你說什么  -我的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出高價讓你排查的那部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說是被我女兒的電腦感染了的那部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但另有人跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是塞勒斯·比尼黑了我的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要么知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么你就是失職了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為我們互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相尊重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地獄里有個特別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是為不支持其他女同胞的惡女準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地獄里也有個差不多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為那些只會用大道理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為自己辯解的女人準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生活真是精彩啊  莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是殺人犯  又是男妓的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至還有副總統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生活不及你的好朋友塞勒斯一半精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在還沒開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統仍然在考慮其它選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為還有其它的還擊方法  不用...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等會再打給你  議員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊麗莎白·諾斯剛剛來找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出事了  我們得做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《時代周刊》剛剛聯系了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詢問有關你照片的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的艷照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片上的男人叫邁克爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為伊麗莎白·諾斯工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是我們自己黨派的  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有別的  伊麗莎白和你的副總統有一腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是哪種意義上都有一腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新聞已經發布了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-連照片一起嗎  -目前只是快報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在我們只能用同性間的性關系來形容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些剛剛泄露給BNC的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}白宮幕僚長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還在指望有證據能證明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人的男妓身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}比尼完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宮方面尚未發表評論
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但對總統來說  這絕不是個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}塞勒斯骯臟的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他已經承受著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對西安哥拉宣戰的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  再說一次  我非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們要怎么辦  -先拖著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宮律師辦公室正在鑒定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些照片的真實性和這件事的法律性質
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你能確認這就是塞勒斯·比尼的艷照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么  難道塞勒斯有個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒見過的雙胞胎兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  阿什莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  西安哥拉  流感恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去打你的流感針吧  大衛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我必須得調查這事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓他去調查  他能找到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當我發現邁克爾為伊麗莎白·諾斯工作的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刪掉了所有的郵件和短信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在看來好像不太明智
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這并不違法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們如果這么做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要面對的可是長達幾個月的國會聽證會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳票  特別檢察官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非律師辦公室給出他們的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞清楚這些照片的性質和來源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我不會發表更多評論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們確定是否要為此抗爭之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能確認或者否認任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要抗爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經起草了一份初步協議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初始期限是三年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邁克爾在每年的婚姻生活中收到一百萬美金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你說什么  -邁克爾得全額退款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上一百萬的罰金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他違反了任何協議條款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密條款  公共形象  隨機的藥物檢測
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  塞勒斯算是買下我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指的是租用的反義詞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚姻是解決這事的唯一辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國人民喜歡這樣的愛情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國人民會為愛原諒所有犯下的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話  這事就是另一樁華盛頓性丑聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  塞勒斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你同意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道你為什么會同意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在是男妓史上最出名的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以寫本書賣給好萊塢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在色情版里傾情出演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫"在塞勒斯·比尼體內"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該最了解我不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一點都不了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,40年來我一直未公開承認同性戀身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,40年來  我和女人發生性關系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在女人的兩腿之間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我自身而言  毫無快感  也不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此期間  我只和兩個男人上過床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一位是我此生摯愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外一位是個男妓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說  后者無可否認是個糟糕的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這種方式...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種方式既殘忍又不公
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉  麗芙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到  我不能這樣對詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要和這個人結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是昨晚所有的監控錄像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前門  后門  衛生間  凡是你想得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-謝謝  -樂意效勞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅文在搞內部清理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密殺令牌  這是B613的收尾流程
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們搞清理不能請搬家公司嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來都有一個計劃預案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防B613的身份遭到泄露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小時前有個人想殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這張牌就是從他身上掉出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎每一位曾效力于B613的特工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在都成了后患
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用數字電臺怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以提醒其他特工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我查過了  已經損壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅文用它聯系那些毫無警惕的特工回總部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后痛下殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈克  查查這些車牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交通攝像頭  加油站攝像頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的攝像  找黑色林肯城市轎車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你要去找羅文嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會來找我的  我打算先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么急找我何事  羅賓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅文正對B613進行內部清理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他鎖定的目標是所有特工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他弄了一副紙牌  牌上印著我們的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要把我們逐一除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得應該讓你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這很好笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想讓我死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真貼心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命都充滿意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我下車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事實上  我們現在當場就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你明白...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命的意義  羅賓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我遲到了嗎  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我追蹤了安德魯  伊麗莎白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫比亞克過去六個月的手機記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到昨晚之前  他們只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時出現在同一個地點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱特琳被謀殺當晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都在杰里米·溫斯洛的律師事務所里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們當晚為什么在那里  他們見面談了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,律所所有的開銷都算在一位客戶的賬上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,訂書釘  鉛筆  甚至空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們能確定是哪位客戶  也許我們就能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-知道他們的談話內容  -很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我黑進了律師事務所的網絡系統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何關于那晚會面的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至沒有他們去過律師事務所的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得進去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打賭肯定有什么書面形式的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,律師們鐘愛紙質文件  就是這么怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家律所的門禁是高端生物識別多重模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們進不去  我們需要指紋才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們確實有根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱特琳那晚去律師事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找她爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定撞見了伊麗莎白·諾斯和副總統
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在秘密會面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當她試圖離開的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和丹·庫比亞克為了那個文件夾發生爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是奧利維亞的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  客戶編號15226
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能查到名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15226  韋科
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韋科  德州城市還是石油公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-拿著  -為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你用得上  -我不需要槍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要槍有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父親在清理后患
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是密殺令牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的不比特工少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你對他來說也是個威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:13:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道怎么開槍  只不過不用而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的整個職業生涯中沒用過槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的整個職業生涯中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒和你父親作對過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸不會殺我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定他想殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我來教你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格洛克26型  半自動手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉起槍  準備射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟  臀部  頭部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣他們就任你宰割了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致命射擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不用非得呆在這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你開口  我就不找你父親了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以收拾行李  遠離這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關上潘多拉魔盒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新回到太陽底下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽很久之前就隕落了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且再也不會升起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我來晚了  有事耽誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有丹·庫比亞克的消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒找到那個白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利維亞·波普咬著我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統也沒下令開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想聊一聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞勒斯·比尼的丑聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會對白宮西廂不利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統已經推動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二任期內的議程來緩和事態了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個黨派內的一些議員和議院領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正強烈敦促塞勒斯·比尼辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您看過尼克松的辭職信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"親愛的國務卿先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我謹辭去美國總統職務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理查德·尼克松謹上"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做總統時最重要的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這么簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們這么辦  -塞勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我提交辭職信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您批準
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就說  "謝謝你一直以來的努力  塞勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很榮幸"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再回答
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"總統先生  感到榮幸的是我"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  我回到辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有個人在那里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他拿走我的徽章  送我上車
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而您呢  先生  立即叫小紅過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討論發表什么樣的聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她會建議您嚴厲譴責我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不同意  但她堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽她的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擊我來為您自己樹立威信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就要開戰了  一場惡戰  愚蠢的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是兩天前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會阻止您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但到了這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了今天  先生  我  今天...    
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我就是個笑話  最可笑的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有發揮一點作用  總統先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在唯一能幫到您的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是離開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"謝謝你一直以來的努力  塞  我很榮幸"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-塞勒斯  -“謝謝你一直以來的努力  塞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很榮幸"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"謝謝你一直以來的努力  塞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很榮幸"  請說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你一直以來的努力  塞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生  感到榮幸的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么總統先生還沒發表聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生目前正在處理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起發生在美國本土的恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正忙于確保該情況不會再次發生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個問題  馬丁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首席檢察官傳喚你是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你回想一下3月25日的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當晚  比恩先生刪除了他和那個被他召來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男妓之間的所有通話記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和電郵往來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-對此你知情嗎  -不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3月25日當晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否曾協助比恩先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毀滅證據
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有那晚的不在場證明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠蘭女士  我正在問你問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3月25日晚上你有不在場證明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請先停止記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我們還是不要問得太細了  大衛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字記錄的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得嚴格一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用太慌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請記住你已宣誓保證所言屬實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再問你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3月25日當晚你有不在場證明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奧·伯爾根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3月25日晚上你和里奧·伯爾根在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-大衛  -惠蘭小姐  現在正在記錄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*...There's only you in my life*
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*The only thing that's right*
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整晚都在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*My first love*
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  惠蘭小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-今天就這樣  -大衛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:19:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*You're every breath that I take*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*You're every step I make*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的電話  查理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*And I*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我關機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*I want to share*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*All my love with you*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*No one else will do*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密殺令牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是B613的收尾流程
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*And your eyes*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*Your eyes, your eyes*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*They tell me how much you care*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*Oh, yes, you will always be*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是來殺我的嗎  -不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}*My endless love*
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是不殺了你  我就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是沒有辦法的  羅賓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿口扯謊的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:19:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9} *Two hearts*
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直沒有動手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你也對此視而不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9} *Two hearts that beat as one*
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9} *Our lives have just begun*
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最惡心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你殺我之前還想上我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我這有發現  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅文的車牌在羅諾克城外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被交通監控捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諾克斯維爾有一個B613的配電站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能是要去那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是要去曼斯菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曼斯菲爾德  小城市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠在外地  7級戒備的安全屋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說得對  就是那了  多謝了  哈克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你來這干什么  -還記得這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底來干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《生命中最重要的歌》
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還記得我第一次放給你聽的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多時候  我并不是個感情用事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情就是弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是盡管你的家人可以變著花樣地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷害你  操縱你  拒不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的成功都是踩著你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但無論你多么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻還是無法抹去那些愉快回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我說過不會再管你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很顯然只有我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才會高興
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從未放手過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永遠都不會不管我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你無處可去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你唯一有的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這段親手塑造的可悲扭曲的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這段你隱藏在暗處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱牽線木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假裝沒有你的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界將不復存在的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:23:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無法改過自新
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成一個正常人  因為  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個病態的孤鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會撒謊  還稱之為愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還有點良心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的骨肉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有我  根本不會有什么奧利維亞·波普
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很難承認
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我是個失敗的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我嘔心瀝血
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背負罵名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是為了保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好讓你覺得自己獨一無二
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但換來的不是感激  而是冷嘲熱諷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個不放過任何機會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使遍渾身解數
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:23:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想殺了自己的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的人生才是可悲的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是不正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是那個不懂愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.13,0:24:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每次看到我都惡心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.88,0:24:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來說破吧  奧利維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.09,0:24:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到的不過是自己罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.14,0:24:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.85,0:24:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當心點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.17,0:25:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在...開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.50,0:25:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.74,0:25:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然對自己父親開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.60,0:25:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然對我開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.48,0:25:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.39,0:25:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的從沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.73,0:25:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會有膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.47,0:25:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扣下板機
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你第一次上幼兒園的前一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.21,0:26:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.51,0:26:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你緊張到睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.44,0:26:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把留聲機拿去你房間
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.69,0:26:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放了這張唱片
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.78,0:26:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史提夫·旺達的歌聲響起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.04,0:26:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有十分鐘  你就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.82,0:26:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你多不愿承認
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.95,0:26:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.02,0:27:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會想我的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.71,0:27:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.94,0:27:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.31,0:27:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的牙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.36,0:27:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新補的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.81,0:27:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.37,0:27:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人想殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.87,0:27:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是該殺你  但我不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.78,0:27:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.38,0:27:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下不了手  羅賓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.83,0:27:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打了我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.50,0:27:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你先打我的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.92,0:27:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶死了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.31,0:27:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗蘭奶奶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.57,0:27:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  什么時候
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.59,0:27:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾周前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.41,0:27:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你知道她病了  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.40,0:27:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道  只是  我沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.42,0:27:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后病情惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.07,0:28:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪她走的  幫了她一把
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.91,0:28:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不想讓她受罪  -當然
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.80,0:28:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.47,0:28:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該多打電話給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.24,0:28:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.29,0:28:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該多打給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.60,0:28:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你毀了一切  查理
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.71,0:28:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好吧  -沒錯  你毀掉了哈克的整個人生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.55,0:28:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.91,0:28:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想或許我可以彌補
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.28,0:28:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.73,0:28:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一些B613的資料  我們的所做作為
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.20,0:28:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到指令將這些文件從儲物柜里偷出來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.06,0:28:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后用空白文件替換
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.57,0:28:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本應該把所有的文件都送還指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.92,0:28:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我私自留一些  你懂的  以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.44,0:28:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為這能幫上忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.29,0:28:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.30,0:28:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.55,0:28:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一些情報
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.53,0:28:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要知道他可能去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.61,0:28:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.38,0:28:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道一些內幕
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.94,0:29:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他將你活生生地囚禁起來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.29,0:29:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他還來探望你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.46,0:29:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一周一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.47,0:29:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-每天  -每天都來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.72,0:29:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他每天都來探望你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.48,0:29:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他對你有種變態扭曲的癡迷
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.49,0:29:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把你囚禁起來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.98,0:29:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天放你出來一次欣賞他囚籠里的寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.06,0:29:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定知道一些內幕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.70,0:29:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你耗費數年的時間監視他
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.98,0:29:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對他的瘋狂行徑了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.17,0:29:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定知道他現在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.22,0:29:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.28,0:29:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就要答案
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.08,0:29:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女兒  你必須向前看
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.84,0:29:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們父女兩總只是互相指責
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.10,0:29:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和他一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.66,0:29:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一點也不像他
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.15,0:29:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.21,0:29:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.88,0:29:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很享受為總統效力
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.34,0:29:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又和B613的人糾纏不清
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.83,0:29:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你四周看看
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.47,0:29:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身陷囹圄  你來探望我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.26,0:29:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算每天都來還是...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.42,0:30:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他毀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.85,0:30:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淚流成河吧  麗芙  隨你便
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.54,0:30:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.89,0:30:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.08,0:30:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.07,0:30:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你辭職了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.01,0:30:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李還真不少
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.54,0:31:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  沒錯  那是詹姆斯的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.26,0:31:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不忍心用
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.97,0:31:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.56,0:31:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去歐洲
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.10,0:31:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐洲人能夠接納失敗與名聲掃地的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.45,0:31:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西恩娜·羅杰斯今早說我是一個"典型同性戀"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.20,0:31:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我辛苦工作  三十年來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.90,0:31:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直奮斗不息才進入了當今權力最大的辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在一切都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.84,0:31:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對著鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.66,0:31:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已認不清自己的面目
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.53,0:31:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個典型的同性戀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.20,0:31:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.13,0:31:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.29,0:31:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你仔細給我聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.98,0:31:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我現在要用我所認識的塞勒斯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.34,0:31:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟人說話的方式來跟你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.87,0:31:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.54,0:31:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么時候決定允許他們打垮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.99,0:31:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.75,0:31:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生活不公平  那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.67,0:31:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活本來就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.09,0:31:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在媒體上戲謔你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.84,0:31:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘲笑你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.73,0:31:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道就傷害了你內心深處脆弱的一面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.02,0:31:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.66,0:32:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情本就如此
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.70,0:32:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你失去了你深愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.81,0:32:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你失去了一個能讓你感受家庭溫暖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.67,0:32:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  猜猜怎么著
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.17,0:32:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟一點  因為這就是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.55,0:32:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認識的塞勒斯·比尼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.62,0:32:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會躲在自己半空的衣櫥里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.44,0:32:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像一個臭婊子嚇得尿褲子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.79,0:32:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認識的塞勒斯是一個愛國者
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.47,0:32:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他咬緊牙關
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.53,0:32:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜一切代價為國家效力
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.56,0:32:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道  此時此刻  你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.41,0:32:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.44,0:32:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所看到這個可悲的身影并不配
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.77,0:32:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在總統辦公室里的總統徽章上面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.18,0:32:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更別說為總統出謀劃策
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.21,0:32:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是誰  塞  -麗芙
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.53,0:32:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是誰  塞  -麗芙
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.84,0:32:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰  塞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.25,0:32:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這個世上最有權力的人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.27,0:32:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.93,0:32:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這個世上最有權力的人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.92,0:32:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  所以你不是什么臭婊子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.47,0:32:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我管理著這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.05,0:32:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不是任何人的婊子  -我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.87,0:32:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看來你還是有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.97,0:32:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是個婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.94,0:32:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就做出點樣子給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.24,0:33:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就證明給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.05,0:33:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看你是誰  塞勒斯·比尼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.91,0:33:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚禮什么時候舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.87,0:33:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-還沒決定  -夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.13,0:33:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  也許是在夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.85,0:33:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得問一個觀眾想知道的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.43,0:33:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們現在已經訂婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.73,0:33:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人可能認為那是為了方便
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.57,0:33:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前很害怕  現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.42,0:33:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這讓我提心吊膽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.64,0:33:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這些照片的流出讓我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.48,0:33:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也瞞不下去了  我也意識到自己不想瞞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.99,0:33:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以為自己違法行為道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.70,0:33:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以為讓總統蒙羞道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.73,0:33:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不能因為自己
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.67,0:33:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墜入情網而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.85,0:33:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他們是靈魂伴侶  -他們是罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.62,0:33:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  塞勒斯·比尼都道歉過了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.79,0:33:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以突然就要免除他的罪責了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.93,0:33:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是賣淫罪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.64,0:33:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對傳統家庭價值觀來說那樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.21,0:33:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別因為你自己嚴格的道德觀就對我不滿  布魯克
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.32,0:33:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就像《風月俏佳人》一樣  多浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.41,0:34:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且早前的民調數據顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.82,0:34:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美國人民都同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.54,0:34:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了你的采訪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.86,0:34:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很感人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.27,0:34:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我娶了個男妓
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.05,0:34:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我知道錢都花在哪兒了  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.86,0:34:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給你倒一杯威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.61,0:34:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能告訴我如何處理西安哥拉問題
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.06,0:34:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杯子在那個箱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.01,0:34:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使共和黨內壓力重重
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.32,0:34:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}格蘭特總統\N發生爆炸案并不意味著需要戰爭來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.91,0:34:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.25,0:34:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕向西安哥拉派遣兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.25,0:34:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自白宮內部的消息強調稱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.76,0:34:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.32,0:34:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在街上聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.54,0:34:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫壓根兒就沒準備打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.05,0:34:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來是那么一回事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.56,0:34:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那意味著什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.31,0:34:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲茨在黨內已經盡失人心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.37,0:34:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是總統先生  莉茲  "菲茨"不是你能叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.71,0:34:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我有得罪過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.89,0:34:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為咱倆已經達成了共識
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.38,0:34:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們都跟安德魯有一腿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.78,0:34:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那并不能使我們成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.47,0:34:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會增加我們患上同一種性病的風險
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.14,0:34:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.74,0:35:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和在我之后的女人都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.29,0:35:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德魯在床上是多么開放
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.70,0:35:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很有奉獻精神  但他很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.76,0:35:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不會是總統之位的有力競爭者
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.46,0:35:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以下一次大選開始時
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.93,0:35:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能賭對人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.49,0:35:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為就上床而言
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.67,0:35:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遠不及安德魯那樣溫和
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.12,0:35:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓你痛不欲生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.78,0:35:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以進去的  波普女士
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.57,0:35:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.99,0:35:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.34,0:36:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你聽聽我的心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.03,0:36:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你被警察抓了我會聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.92,0:36:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我要報警了  -拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.29,0:36:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你知道為什么我會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.48,0:36:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你看看這些
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.35,0:36:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看就好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.57,0:36:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這會是我請求你做的最后一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.05,0:36:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奎恩  你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.05,0:36:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.45,0:36:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經搞明白了  韋科
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.50,0:36:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是城市名  這是個首字母縮略詞
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.93,0:36:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,WACO
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.36,0:36:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西安哥拉商業組織
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.88,0:36:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個西安哥拉政府的附屬機構
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.31,0:36:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰里米·溫斯洛的律所幫他們管理在美國的資產
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.11,0:36:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生  謝謝你能見我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.74,0:37:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能坐下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.54,0:37:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西安哥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.75,0:37:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個炸副總統的國家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.23,0:37:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他  你可能記得
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.20,0:37:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我們一個同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.28,0:37:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得那是巧合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.31,0:37:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.65,0:37:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西安哥拉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.14,0:37:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望自己大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.00,0:37:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對大多數政府來說
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.75,0:37:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人想殺副總統  他們會還以顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.86,0:37:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不屬于大多數中的一員對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.83,0:37:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.78,0:37:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他往柱子后面站的時候特意確認了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.15,0:37:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看他  他換了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.41,0:37:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像他知道在那里才安全
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.64,0:37:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道會有爆炸發生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.13,0:37:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著我被炸飛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.37,0:37:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你而言應該夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.08,0:37:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是  你甚至根本不在乎我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.17,0:37:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或許也知道這點
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.48,0:37:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我早就知道你會作何反應
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.63,0:37:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們想這樣開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.11,0:37:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那為什么要拍麗芙的照片  -不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.81,0:37:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個謎團中只有這一點還說不通了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.71,0:37:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來得正是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.36,0:37:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.07,0:37:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.57,0:38:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在亞當斯摩根一個非常小的紅酒店里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.66,0:38:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了杜貝萊酒  竟然有兩瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.54,0:38:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗芙  我需要跟你談談你父親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.69,0:38:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想談我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.14,0:38:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還給你買了啤酒...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.54,0:38:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是進口的  賣的人說你肯定會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.25,0:38:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但鑒于是啤酒  所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.62,0:38:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗芙  我抓到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.35,0:38:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抓到你父親了  然后又讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.73,0:38:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  烤箱里在加熱你愛吃的漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.09,0:38:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還去那家用第一夫人名字
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.50,0:38:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給派命名的披薩店
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.70,0:38:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買了個朵莉·麥迪遜[第四屆總統夫人]
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.09,0:38:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就松開褲腰帶敞開肚皮吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.23,0:38:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-麗芙  -我不想談我父親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.34,0:38:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想談論他了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.38,0:38:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對這些唱片簡直著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.51,0:38:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個專輯  簡直太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.22,0:38:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我差點就抓到他了  -別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.71,0:38:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這張  這張是我最喜歡的之一
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.17,0:38:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗芙
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.76,0:38:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-跟我一起跳舞  -但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.55,0:38:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經走了  我們不關心
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.89,0:38:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.64,0:39:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗芙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.21,0:39:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.85,0:40:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  我好愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.01,0:40:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要佛蒙特的菲茨
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.33,0:40:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.34,0:40:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要陽光下的你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.62,0:40:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.58,0:40:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.32,0:40:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是選擇杰克  也不是選擇菲茨
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.61,0:40:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我選自己
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.51,0:40:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我選擇奧利維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.03,0:40:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在  奧利維亞正在跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.38,0:40:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在跳舞  杰克  我好自由
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.12,0:40:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要么跟我一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.17,0:40:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么離開我的舞池
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.90,0:40:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己一個人跳沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.66,0:41:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒在鋼琴上跟人做過愛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.83,0:41:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.84,0:41:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會很滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.63,0:41:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿條毯子
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.30,0:41:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.42,0:41:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還能去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.44,0:41:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不我再拿個枕頭吧  當墊子用
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.33,0:41:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我們是不是該在鋼琴邊上做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.87,0:41:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一我們倆都爬到鋼琴上
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.76,0:41:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那玩意兒壓垮了怎么辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.52,0:41:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一  聲音會很大
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.86,0:41:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二  會很疼  而且不好向救護人員解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.09,0:41:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我還是愿意試試
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.64,0:41:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我們倆都精力旺盛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.93,0:41:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你說  我們絕對能搞壞一架鋼琴的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.62,0:41:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說我是不是太自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.45,0:41:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗芙
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.35,0:41:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我  總統先生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.45,0:41:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界上有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.46,0:41:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你離開就活不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.88,0:41:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么  如果我們奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.76,0:41:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會不惜一切奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.06,0:42:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對她做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.46,0:42:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.01,0:42:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在覺得這場戰爭如何  總統先生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.28,0:42:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗芙
